Package: markovRt
Title: Make Random Art Based on Markov Chains
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Lars", "Kulbe", , "lars.kulbe@student.uvannl", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package creates some random artpieces based on a very simplified Markov chain. In the current version, square and rectangular canvases are supported.The canvas is filled from the inside out using a spiral traversal algorithm. Plotting is done using the base R 'graphics' package and 'viridisLite' colour pallets.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
